&quot;_**SuzukiSw1ft** will recieve no S for some reason_&quot;
I was really confused as you could see, but I was more confused in the second image ( http://imgur.com/a/9AQWd)  when he typed in chat and he still had the italic and bold name.
Has anyone else seen this happen before or even have the ability to do this? I&#039;m just really curious about how can someone have bold and italics as a name but only in chat, champ select and in-game he had a normal name like everyone else, it was only after the game.

Thanks for reading and hopefully helping me out
~Rexisea {{champion:17}}
